result.name: Pizza Hut Hong Kong

reviews.text: Coming from the land of fast food (USA) dropped in for a pizza or two. The setup is a bit different from abroad, quite nice for a fast food place. Pizzas were good but I'm a Chicago deep dish guy with a beer or 2! But if you in the neighborhood, drop in for a pizza or two. Service was friendly and quick! Price was comparable with USA.. Go Golden State Warriors!
A good choice in Tin Shui Wai if you want to meet with friends in a quiet and neat restaurant. Staff are friendly and food is standard.

Loved this Pizza Hut. We stayed in the resort for a week and ate here twice. Primarily we went twice because of the amazing service from our waitress on the first night, Mon. She was incredible at her job, helpful and so friendly. Food was predictably nice but Mon made this our favorite Pizza Hut.
